Arim is the Amateur Radio Instant Messaging program for use with
the ARDOP TNC.

The latest version can always be found at:

  https://www.whitemesa.net/arim/arim.html

Visit this page for documentation and source code downloads.

For support, news and updates, join one or both of these Groups.io groups:

  * arim-ham
    For users of ARIM and gARIM. Latest source code distribution found here.
    https://groups.io/g/arim-ham

  * ardop users group
    General discussion on the ARDOP TNC and related software.
    https://ardop.groups.io/g/users

